<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Operation: Save the BBQ!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>[ SYSTEM COMPROMISED ]</h1>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Operation: Save the BBQ!</h2>
            <p>Greetings, student.</p>
            <p>The notorious hacker group "The Vegan Vanguard" has breached the Mediacollege Amsterdam servers. They have encrypted the location and time of the end-of-year BBQ!</p>
            <p>It's up to you to hack into the compromised systems, find the flags, and save the BBQ. Put your OWASP Top 10 knowledge to the test.</p>
            
            <form action="/login-student" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="studentId">Enter your Student Number (e.g. 123456) to begin your mission:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="studentId" name="studentId" required autocomplete="off">
                </div>
                <button type="submit">Initialize Uplink</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
